        {
            "title": "歐洲股市回吐漲幅 航空股下跌抵消媒體和科技股漲勢",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"837\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/O_AoMRzl1FpysdVvU8afRw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgzNw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0c31c7f27ed62cc0954417d520f65974\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐洲股市回吐漲幅，航空股下跌抵消媒體和科技股的上漲，與此同時，投資者正在消化大量公司業績。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"斯托克\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:斯托克;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/斯托克\">斯托克</a>600指數收盤基本持平，盤中一度上漲0.5%。航空股下跌，此前易捷航空發布盈利預警，其股價一度下跌8.8%，創2022年6月以來最大盤中跌幅，隨後跌幅收窄至5.0%。瑞安航空和德國漢莎航空等其他航空股也下跌，拖累斯托克600旅遊和休閒板塊轉跌。該板塊成為斯托克600指數中表現最差的板塊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">媒體和科技板塊表現出色，CTS Eventim AG和Nemetschek SE漲幅均超過2%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e5912392-eb97-311a-bbb6-8b7c083afbd9-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者正在尋求更多證據，以評估伊朗戰爭對企業銷售和利潤的影響。將在未來三周內公佈業績的公司，其市值占斯托克600指數的60%以上。目前該指數仍低於戰前水平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「財報季可能會引發歐洲市場進一步波動，」Hargreaves Lansdown首席投資策略師Emma Wall表示。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"837\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DgHFCtON6dv1nEMgUeSrgA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgzNw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/483dadc8ff7fa2fad90e7888ac5a651a\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題European Stocks Stall as Airline Losses Offset Media, Tech Gains</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%9B%9E%E5%90%90%E6%BC%B2%E5%B9%85-%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E8%82%A1%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C%E6%8A%B5%E6%B6%88%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E5%92%8C%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E8%82%A1%E6%BC%B2%E5%8B%A2-172619208.html",
