        {
            "title": "伊朗戰事加劇中期選舉壓力 川普赴西部搖擺州力推經濟議程",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Photographer: David Paul Morris/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7e4a8i45ktq.Etj269Lphw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1e83bbdd98beee16ce2b275fb8a1a91b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: David Paul Morris/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統唐納德·川普計畫前往西部州進行經濟宣講，此時隨著11月中期選舉臨近，白宮正竭力應對愈發失去民心的伊朗戰爭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普本周訪問的內華達州和亞利桑那州是他在2024年大選中拿下的搖擺州，此行反映出政府內部及國會共和黨人日益意識到，對於面對沉重生活成本壓力的美國居民，該黨必須提醒他們關注取得的經濟成就。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白宮新聞秘書卡羅琳·萊維特表示，川普周四將在拉斯維加斯舉行的圓桌會議上重點宣傳其核心稅改法案，並提醒選民們民主黨人一致反對該法案。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dd3e4887-be9e-361a-bf89-a7d29410357e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她在周三的新聞發布會上對記者稱：「國會民主黨人一再證明，他們是可負擔性方面的騙子，他們認為政府應從美國人民辛苦賺來的收入中拿走更多。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白宮試圖將焦點轉向國內議題之際，伊朗戰爭仍在衝擊金融市場，外交解決方案仍難覓。民調顯示，多數美國人不認可川普對戰爭的處理方式，並將汽油價格上漲歸咎於他。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Photographer: David Paul Morris/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9IyZOY3IL_f1S.xGzqtA8Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/20eedd7b728ff94666e31b3d995e9302\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: David Paul Morris/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而，共和黨面臨的最大挑戰之一在於川普本人。這位美國總統在經濟活動中經常脫離主題，轉而談論伊朗戰爭、政敵、媒體以及白宮翻修計畫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周，包括參議院多數黨領袖約翰·圖恩在內的多名共和黨人呼籲川普制定結束戰爭的計畫，並指出霍爾木茲海峽的關閉正使消費者和農民承受壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於在為汽油、醫療和其他商品成本苦苦掙扎的選民來說，川普的經濟宣傳可能難以產生吸引力。他們收到的退稅金額雖高於去年，但遠低於川普在報稅季前所承諾的水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國稅局數據顯示，今年領取退稅的人數多於去年，平均退稅金額比2025年高出近350美元。但這僅約為川普承諾的1000美元平均漲幅的三分之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另有早期跡象表明納稅人幾乎沒有察覺到成長。兩黨政策中心近期一項民調顯示，僅有27%的受訪者表示去年的稅改令其受益，24%的人表示受損，38%的人表示沒有區別。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">參議院金融委員會民主黨最高成員Ron Wyden周三表示：「現實情況是，對於絕大多數勞動者來說，這項稅法並未產生實際效果。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Turns From Iran to Economy as GOP Faces Midterm Headwinds</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%88%B0%E4%BA%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%9F%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%B5%B4%E8%A5%BF%E9%83%A8%E6%90%96%E6%93%BA%E5%B7%9E%E5%8A%9B%E6%8E%A8%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E8%AD%B0%E7%A8%8B-171324479.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 01:49:57",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "Polaris股價飆升10%,公司無懼關稅逆風",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Wn.rYUWN1hqAlMLBctbzFQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEB0507V_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - Polaris Inc. (NYSE:PII) 股價週四大漲10%,此前該公司表示,近期關稅政策變化不會對其3月3日發布的2026年財務指引產生重大影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家動力運動產品製造商表示,預計關稅變化(不包括潛在退款)對其全年展望不會產生重大影響。此前,競爭對手BRP Inc. (NASDAQ:DOO) 週三因美國關稅政策變化而暫停其2027財年指引,導致Polaris股價下跌。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7621d93c-c1b4-3a15-86c0-9648737e0647-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Polaris強調其作為唯一一家總部位於美國的大型動力運動產品公司的地位,並擁有大量本土製造業務。該公司在阿拉巴馬州、印第安納州和明尼蘇達州設有生產設施。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司表示,正持續加強與國內供應商的關係。Polaris計劃於4月28日週二的第一季度財報電話會議上提供更多細節。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/polaris%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%8710-%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E9%80%86%E9%A2%A8-155828953.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 00:28:04",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
